            "title": "盤中速報 - 新興(2605)股價殺至跌停，跌停價28.4元，成交69,150張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2605-TW</a>)05日11:39下跌3.15元，股價跌停報28.4元，委買2,099張、委賣87張，成交69,150張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為船務代理業。拖船駁船業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2605-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲24.7%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.88%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+13,143 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+5,950 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+7,193 張</li> <li>融資增減：+4,573 張</li> <li>融券增減：+454 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
