            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)05日11:17上漲19.5元，股價漲停報218.0元，委買272張、委賣7,516張，成交62,510張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為PCB製造。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>欣興(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3037:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3037\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3037-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲6.15%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.88%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+29,646 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+25,341 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+3,405 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+900 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,005 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1,201 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
